Package: nichevol
Type: Package
Title: An R package for assessment of evolution of ecological niches considering uncertainty in niche reconstructions
Version: 0.1.13
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marlon E.", "Cobos", email = "manubio13@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Hannah L.", "Owens", email = "hannah.owens@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("A. Townsend", "Peterson", email = "town@ku.edu", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Marlon E. Cobos <manubio13@gmail.com>
Date: 2019-09-25
Description: This package helps to perform critical steps in the process of 
    assessment of evolution of species ecological niches, with uncertainty 
    incorporated in reconstructions. The main analyses include: initial exploration 
    of environmental data in species records and accessible areas, preparation of 
    data for phylogenetic analyses, phylogenetic analyses of ecological niches, and 
    plotting for interpretations.
